title: Avengers: The Terminatrix Objective (Archive|1993|Kritter-DCP)
description:
This was a limited four-issue miniseries from 1993. Promotional info - "The sequel to Citizen Kang guest stars Thunderstrike, USAgent, and War machine! Terminatrix attempts to expand Chronopolis beyond Kang's seven-millennium boundaries and discovers a shocking secret about time!"

This is the one-volume DCP Archive Edition compiled by Kritter-DCP. There is no digital release so far of these issues so these scans are the best available at the moment. Thanks to Kritter for his efforts, please seed and enjoy! :-)
